headline: Booking’s Fintech Boss on the Strategic Importance of Its ‘Very Profitable’ Payments Biz
summary: Saving a basis point or two per transaction in Booking.com's payments business can turn into a windfall of millions of dollars. That's an edge that Booking.com is leveraging in payments, which are also central to its connected trip strategy.
